{"tid":505604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【修議規戰】梁國雄提司法覆核 指修訂違《基本法》","createTime":"2017-12-21T09:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T14:16:41.000Z","uid":35790,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b5f5242e9798b4625106b3ac799fd3f56b57a548","tid":505604,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"【修議規戰】梁國雄提司法覆核 指修訂違《基本法》<br />\n<br />\n即時要聞  2017-12-21 17:37:01 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n立法會上周通過建制派提出的《議事規則》修訂，其中有關全體委員大會法定人數由35人減至20人，前立法會議會梁國雄今向高院提出司法覆核，控告立法會主席梁君彥，指有關修訂違反《基本法》第75條，要求法庭頒令有關修定違憲。<br />\n<br />\n《基本法》第75條列明「香港特別行政區立法會舉行會議的法定人數為不少於全體議員的二分之一。立法會議事規則由立法會自行制定，但不得與本法相抵觸」。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"ce1c6ddcf03ab0ab51f5555ea74c917840c30266","tid":505604,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T09:49:02.000Z","msg":"基本法最終解釋權及修改權在人大"},{"pid":"6f9b80654e65c3dfdbe7ad0687a83be1ad6b6dd6","tid":505604,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T09:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個法源頭係邊？釋一釋就得"},{"pid":"74c08858b3243a9cc960d5ed82dca93c10a48ccf","tid":505604,"uid":49279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T09:59:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個法源頭係邊？釋一釋就得</blockquote><br />\n香港基本法起草委員會名單　李柱銘 司徒華　"},{"pid":"8af47007391f7e58cca71b2e20a28ef256e6e6e3","tid":505604,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:06:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個法源頭係邊？釋一釋就得</blockquote><br />\n立法會有咩用？"},{"pid":"214aee6e3c50f1d43c7b3730739a4d95e4329617","tid":505604,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T10:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbf38446e86754586bd7e1cb032835235171f5a","tid":505604,"uid":57705,"like":